    "info_cards": {
      "type": "info-cards",
      "blocks": {
        "infocard_1": {
          "type": "infocard",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/C8257.avif",
            "hide_image": false,
            "product": "",
            "caption": "",
            "title": "The Tree You See Is the Tree You Get",
            "text": "<p>Each Java Tree in our collection is <strong>individually photographed and listed</strong>, ensuring you receive the <em>exact</em> tree you select—nothing random and no surprises. We believe transparency matters when choosing a unique, natural product for your bird. Because every Java Tree is naturally shaped by the environment, they vary in <strong>branch structure, texture, thickness, and climbing angles</strong>. By showing you the actual tree, we allow you to confidently choose the perfect match for your parrot’s <strong>size, personality, mobility, and enrichment needs</strong>.</p><p>Our one-tree-one-photo approach also supports better <strong>cage setup planning</strong>, as you can assess branch orientation, potential toy placement, and stability before your order even arrives. This level of detail is especially valuable for owners of <strong>African Greys, Macaws, Amazons, Conures, Cockatoos</strong>, and other species with varying preferences. With complete visual accuracy, you can trust that the Java Tree delivered to your home is <em>exactly</em> the handcrafted, one-of-a-kind piece you selected—no substitutions, no second-guessing. This commitment to transparency sets Squawk Shop apart and gives you total peace of mind when investing in high-quality, natural bird furniture.</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "infocards_background_color": "#ffffff",
            "infocards_color": "#2f3d45"
          }
        },
        "infocard_2": {
          "type": "infocard",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/01602464.jpg",
            "hide_image": false,
            "product": "",
            "caption": "",
            "title": "Supports Natural Instincts",
            "text": "<p>Our Java Trees are intentionally designed to promote your parrot’s <strong>instinctive behaviors</strong>, including climbing, chewing, balancing, foraging, and exploring. Crafted from <strong>real coffee wood</strong>, each tree offers an organic structure that mimics the branches, textures, and irregular surfaces parrots experience in the wild. This encourages essential daily activities that support <strong>physical strength, coordination, mental stimulation, and emotional well-being</strong>.</p><p>The variety of branch angles and thicknesses helps strengthen grip, balance, and foot health, while the natural bark invites safe chewing that keeps beaks healthy and active. These trees are also ideal for <strong>toy rotation, foraging setups, and multi-level play</strong>, allowing you to build a dynamic enrichment environment that evolves with your bird’s needs. Whether your bird is high-energy, shy, playful, or highly intelligent, these natural structures provide a soothing and instinct-satisfying space that reduces boredom and destructive behaviors. Each tree is more than décor—it’s a daily enrichment tool that supports a <strong>healthier, happier, and more fulfilled bird</strong>.</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "infocards_background_color": "#ffffff",
            "infocards_color": "#2f3d45"
          }
        },
        "infocard_3": {
          "type": "infocard",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Untitled_design_5.png",
            "hide_image": false,
            "product": "",
            "caption": "",
            "title": "Crafted for Strength & Stability",
            "text": "<p>Every Java Tree is built using <strong>dense, durable, sustainably sourced coffee wood</strong>, renowned for its incredible strength and ability to withstand the daily activity of parrots of all sizes. This natural hardwood offers exceptional stability, ensuring your tree remains secure even during vigorous climbing, wing-flapping, chewing, or jumping sessions. The handcrafted base provides additional grounding, giving your bird a confident, wobble-free platform that supports safe movement and long-term use.</p><p>The structure of each tree is carefully evaluated to ensure balanced branch distribution and optimal weight support. Whether you have a <strong>Macaw, Cockatoo, Amazon, African Grey, or small-to-medium species</strong>, your bird can enjoy a dependable, long-lasting play environment designed to handle years of active enrichment. Coffee wood is naturally resistant to cracking and pests, making it one of the safest and most resilient materials for bird stands. Our dedication to durability means you’re investing in a perch that prioritizes safety, longevity, and daily performance—giving both you and your bird complete confidence during every play session.</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "infocards_background_color": "#ffffff",
            "infocards_color": "#2f3d45"
          }
        },
        "infocard_4": {
          "type": "infocard",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Squawk_Shop_Elegant_Cage_Java_Tree_in_Home.jpg",
            "hide_image": false,
            "product": "",
            "caption": "",
            "title": "Beautiful in Any Space",
            "text": "<p>Each Java Tree is a <strong>true work of natural artistry</strong>, featuring organic branch patterns and a sculptural silhouette that adds warmth and beauty to any home. Hand-selected for aesthetic appeal as well as function, these trees serve as both a <strong>design statement and a purpose-driven enrichment tool</strong>. The natural grain, subtle curves, and elegant wood tones complement a wide variety of interior styles, from modern to rustic, without clashing with your décor.</p><p>Beyond appearance, these trees create a visual focal point that celebrates your bird’s presence in your home. They elevate your living space with the look and feel of <strong>real nature</strong>, adding texture and character while maintaining practicality. Because each Java Tree is completely one-of-a-kind, no two homes will ever have the same piece—making it a personalized enhancement to your environment. With the perfect blend of function and beauty, our Java Trees transform your home into a <strong>natural sanctuary</strong> where your bird can thrive while you enjoy an aesthetically pleasing, high-quality centerpiece.</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "infocards_background_color": "#ffffff",
            "infocards_color": "#2f3d45"
          }
        }
      },
